room_title: Escape room "Heroes in Training" by Riddler's Escape in St. Cloud
room_address: 510 25th Ave N, Suite 8 St Cloud, MN 56303
room_description: Your comic book superheroes have disappeared and the Heroes In Training program is urgently seeking brave, intelligent, charismatic applicants to fill their boots. Only those of the highest caliber need apply. Your mission? Find the Villain, stop his reign of terror, and make sure your first H.I.T. Mission, isn't your last.
